{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund access to regular heart health checks & improve awareness of heart health",
        "additional_details": "We think there aren't enough checks and regular testing being done for the heart. Heart disease is one of the biggest killers. My younger brother passed away in his sleep at age 33 due to a heart problem which he never knew about. More needs to be done.",
        "background": "Fund regular heart health checks every 2-3 years to improve early detection of heart defects. Increase awareness of symptoms and risk factors.",
